name: ExtensionCompartmentDefinition_Resource
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.CompartmentDefinition.resource` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `CompartmentDefinition.resource` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `CompartmentDefinition.resource` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`CompartmentDefinition.resource` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `CompartmentDefinition.resource` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `CompartmentDefinition.resource` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `CompartmentDefinition.resource` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `CompartmentDefinition.resource` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `CompartmentDefinition.resource`, but has no comparisons.
